question: What fast food restaurant can I find along the way to Atlantic Works Gallery, East Boston, MA within 180 kilometers from Plaistow Emergency Room, Plaistow, NH?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.104578 42.820057)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.042044 42.372159)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.104578 42.820057)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.104578 42.820057)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.description: Dunkin’ 290 Route 130 Trade Winds Plz Sandwich, MA 02563
